Tested 7 properties on fire.testutils.ChangeDirectory - all passed ✅

**Summary:**
- Analyzed the fire.testutils module which contains utility functions for Python Fire testing
- Focused on the ChangeDirectory context manager as the main testable component
- Successfully tested multiple properties:
  - Round-trip property (directory restoration)
  - Invariant during context (correct directory during execution)
  - Yield value correctness
  - Invalid path handling (including null characters)
  - Nested context managers
  - File path rejection
  - Sequential directory changes

All property-based tests passed without finding any bugs. The ChangeDirectory function correctly implements its documented behavior as a context manager that changes directories and restores the original on exit.
